-- Baylor’s First Heisman Trophy Winner Robert Griffin III to Enter NFL Draft
-- B y   E r i k   M a t u s z e w s k i
-- 2012-01-11T21:16:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-11/baylor-s-first-heisman-trophy-winner-robert-griffin-iii-to-enter-nfl-draft.html
Robert Griffin III will enter this
year’s National Football League draft after a season in which
he became the first Heisman Trophy winner in the 110-year
history of the Baylor University football program.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Erik Matuszewski in New York at 
